Title: Jeg skal forklare alt
Actors: Josefine Frida Pettersen, Thomas Hayes, Ulrikke Falch, Lisa Teige
Plot: Eskild and Linn try to cheer Noora up, but she is still dealing with last Friday. Noora reluctantly goes to Eva to celebrate May the 17th, the National Day. She also decides to confront Nikolai, to find out exactly what happened.
